pullRequest.title: Chore/test coverage/management resource
pullRequest.bodyText:
Checklist

 Server: I added multiple integration tests (Spring) related to the features

Motivation and Context


This PR increases the test coverage of Management and Audit resources from 37% and 10% to 100% (both). All REST endpoints are covered now.

commit.message: Add test case to get all audit events
Add test cases for getting all audit events by date
Load data for findAll and extended test case
Add database reset to the tests

nodes.bodyText: please do not use a SpyBean here. This significantly increases test execution costs and we absolutely want to avoid it for simple cases in which we can easily avoid this!
reset the status of the FeatureToggle
Please test that at least 5 secured REST calls for the Feature Toggles work when the feature is enabled, and do not work (return FORBIDDEN), when the feature is disabled
